channel.title: Designed a website? Need a domain?
channel.description: If you have ACTUALLY DESIGNED a website, and have it hosted at a free domain host(or paid), you can have the domain runeug.com I have tried giving it away before but there have been some other problems, and they could not accept the domain. If you would like it, please let me know the nameservers of the free host that you are using (or paid) in this thread and the domain is yours. This will be judged on a "first post, first serve" basis lol... The reason I am doing this is because I don't want it, and I don't want to cancel, it so I thought I could make use of it. :)
